replies.body:
Probably more than 9 out of 10 people I meet are kind to me. Which is saying something, because I am overweight and unimportant.

I do not see the real world as a toxic place, and most certainly less so than the internet. If you are surrounded by people treating you so badly I would consider a move if it is financially feasible, because your life doesn't have to be like that.

{{sticker:vlad-salute}}
